Story &amp; Profile Viewer</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"View Instagram stories, posts, followers and highlights anonymously. No login required.\"/><meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"instagram viewer,anonymous instagram,instagram story viewer,instagram profile viewer\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"InstaPvStory - Anonymous Instagram Story &amp; Profile Viewer\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"View Instagram stories, posts, followers and highlights anonymously. No login required.\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"InstaPvStory - Anonymous Instagram Story &amp; Profile Viewer\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"View Instagram stories, posts, followers and highlights anonymously. No login required.\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.0x3dzn~oxb6tn.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03~yq9q893hmn.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"app-wrapper\" style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;min-height:100vh\"><header class=\"Header-module__85i50G__header\"><div class=\"Header-module__85i50G__inner\"><a class=\"Header-module__85i50G__logo\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"Header-module__85i50G__logoIcon\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"4\" fill=\"white\" opacity=\"0.95\"></circle><path d=\"M4 20c0-4 3.6-7 8-7s8 3 8 7\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" opacity=\"0.8\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"Header-module__85i50G__logoText\">InstaPvStory</span></a><nav class=\"Header-module__85i50G__nav\"><a class=\"Header-module__85i50G__navLink Header-module__85i50G__active\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"Header-module__85i50G__navLink \" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a><a class=\"Header-module__85i50G__navLink \" href=\"/features\">Features</a><a class=\"Header-module__85i50G__navLink \" href=\"/about\">About</a><span class=\"Header-module__85i50G__divider\"></span><button class=\"Header-module__85i50G__loginBtn\"><svg width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M4 20c0-4 3.6-7 8-7s8 3 8 7\"></path></svg>Login</button></nav><button class=\"Header-module__85i50G__hamburger \" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><span class=\"Header-module__85i50G__hamburgerLine\"></span><span class=\"Header-module__85i50G__hamburgerLine\"></span><span class=\"Header-module__85i50G__hamburgerLine\"></span></button></div></header><div class=\"Header-module__85i50G__mobileMenu \" role=\"navigation\"><nav class=\"Header-module__85i50G__mobileNavLinks\"><a class=\"Header-module__85i50G__mobileNavLink Header-module__85i50G__mobileNavLinkActive\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"Header-module__85i50G__mobileNavLink \" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a><a class=\"Header-module__85i50G__mobileNavLink \" href=\"/features\">Features</a><a class=\"Header-module__85i50G__mobileNavLink \" href=\"/about\">About</a></nav><div class=\"Header-module__85i50G__mobileDivider\"></div><button class=\"Header-module__85i50G__mobileLoginBtn\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M4 20c0-4 3.6-7 8-7s8 3 8 7\"></path></svg>Login</button></div><main style=\"flex:1\"><main><div class=\"Hero-module__i8cThW__heroWrap\"><div class=\"Hero-module__i8cThW__heroBg\"></div><div class=\"Hero-module__i8cThW__heroContent\"><div class=\"Hero-module__i8cThW__welcomeBanner\"><p class=\"Hero-module__i8cThW__welcomeText\">👋 Welcome to InstaPvStory!</p><p class=\"Hero-module__i8cThW__welcomeSub\">View public stories, posts and followers anonymously.</p></div><div class=\"Hero-module__i8cThW__searchContainer\"><div class=\"Hero-module__i8cThW__searchBox\"><input type=\"text\" class=\"Hero-module__i8cThW__searchInput\" placeholder=\"username or profile link\" autoComplete=\"off\" value=\"\"/><button class=\"Hero-module__i8cThW__submitBtn\">Submit</button></div></div><div class=\"Hero-module__i8cThW__historyBar \"><div class=\"Hero-module__i8cThW__historyLabel\">History</div><div class=\"Hero-module__i8cThW__historyChevron\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"></polyline></svg></div></div></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__sections\"><section class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__section\" id=\"features\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__container\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__sectionHead\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__badge\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" style=\"margin-right:6px;vertical-align:middle\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg>Features</span><h2 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__sectionTitle\">Everything You Need,<br/><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__grad\">Zero Compromises</span></h2><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__sectionSub\">A fully-featured anonymous Instagram viewer built on high-performance cloud technology. No shortcuts. No nonsense.</p></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featuresGrid\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureCard MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureLarge\" style=\"--accent:#7c3aed\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureIcon\"><svg width=\"32\" height=\"32\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z\"></path><path d=\"M12 8v4\"></path><path d=\"M12 16h.01\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureTitle\">100% Anonymous</h3><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureDesc\">Browse any public Instagram profile without ever logging in. Your identity stays completely hidden — no traces, no footprints.</p><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureGlow\"></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureCard \" style=\"--accent:#06b6d4\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureIcon\"><svg width=\"32\" height=\"32\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><polygon points=\"13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2\"></polygon></svg></div><h3 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureTitle\">Instant Results</h3><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureDesc\">Real-time data fetched in milliseconds. No delays, no loading spinners.</p><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureGlow\"></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureCard \" style=\"--accent:#f59e0b\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureIcon\"><svg width=\"32\" height=\"32\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polygon points=\"10 8 16 12 10 16 10 8\"></polygon></svg></div><h3 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureTitle\">Stories &amp; Reels</h3><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureDesc\">Watch full stories and play reels with sound. Direct access to all public content.</p><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureGlow\"></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureCard \" style=\"--accent:#10b981\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureIcon\"><svg width=\"32\" height=\"32\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"11\" width=\"18\" height=\"11\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureTitle\">Zero Login Required</h3><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureDesc\">We never ask for your Instagram credentials. Your account is never at risk.</p><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureGlow\"></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureCard \" style=\"--accent:#ec4899\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureIcon\"><svg width=\"32\" height=\"32\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><line x1=\"2\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"22\" y2=\"12\"></line><path d=\"M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureTitle\">Works Worldwide</h3><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureDesc\">Access any public profile from around the globe — no regional restrictions.</p><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureGlow\"></div></div></div></div></section><div style=\"text-align:center;padding:8px 24px 0\"></div><section class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__section\" id=\"how-it-works\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__container\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__sectionHead\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__badge\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" style=\"margin-right:6px;vertical-align:middle\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\"></circle><path d=\"M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 0 1 0 2.83 2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0 2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83l.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33-1.82 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 0 1-2-2 2 2 0 0 1 2-2h.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83 2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0l.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82.33H9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1-1.51V3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2 2 2 0 0 1 2 2v.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0 2 2 0 0 1 0 2.83l-.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33 1.82V9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.51 1H21a2 2 0 0 1 2 2 2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51 1z\"></path></svg>Process</span><h2 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__sectionTitle\">How InstaPVStory<br/><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__grad\">Works</span></h2><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__sectionSub\">Three steps to completely anonymous Instagram browsing.</p></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stepsWrap\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stepCard\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stepNum\">01</div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stepIcon\"><svg width=\"40\" height=\"40\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"8\"></circle><line x1=\"21\" y1=\"21\" x2=\"16.65\" y2=\"16.65\"></line></svg></div><h3 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stepTitle\">Enter a Username</h3><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stepDesc\">Type any public Instagram username into the search bar above. No account needed.</p><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stepConnector\"></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stepCard\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stepNum\">02</div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stepIcon\"><svg width=\"40\" height=\"40\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><polyline points=\"22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12\"></polyline></svg></div><h3 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stepTitle\">Fetch Real Data</h3><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stepDesc\">We instantly query secure data sources and retrieve live profile data, posts, and stories.</p><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stepConnector\"></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stepCard\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stepNum\">03</div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stepIcon\"><svg width=\"40\" height=\"40\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stepTitle\">Browse Anonymously</h3><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stepDesc\">View their photos, reels, stories, follower counts, and bio. All without them knowing.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__section MarketingSections-module__jODscW__comparisonSection\" id=\"why-us\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__container\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__sectionHead\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__badge\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" style=\"margin-right:6px;vertical-align:middle\"><path d=\"M22 6s-2-2-4-2H6C4 4 2 6 2 6s1 4 4 4h12c3 0 4-4 4-4z\"></path><path d=\"M12 10v12\"></path><path d=\"M8 22h8\"></path></svg>Comparison</span><h2 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__sectionTitle\">Why We&#x27;re Better<br/><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__grad\">Than The Rest</span></h2><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__sectionSub\">Most Instagram &quot;viewers&quot; are scraper bots in disguise. We built something different.</p></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__comparisonTableWrapper\"><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__scrollHint\">← Scroll to compare →</p><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__comparisonScroll\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__comparisonTable\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__tableRow MarketingSections-module__jODscW__tableHeader\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureLabel\">Feature</div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__competitorCol\">Logged-in App</div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__competitorCol\">Other Viewer Sites</div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__competitorCol MarketingSections-module__jODscW__ourCol\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__ourBadge\">Best Choice</div>InstaPSV</div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__tableRow\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureLabel\">Visible to Owner</div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__competitorCol\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__tick\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"></polyline></svg></span></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__competitorCol\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__cross\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><line x1=\"18\" y1=\"6\" x2=\"6\" y2=\"18\"></line><line x1=\"6\" y1=\"6\" x2=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></span></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__competitorCol MarketingSections-module__jODscW__ourCol\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__cross\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><line x1=\"18\" y1=\"6\" x2=\"6\" y2=\"18\"></line><line x1=\"6\" y1=\"6\" x2=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></span></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__tableRow\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureLabel\">Login Required</div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__competitorCol\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__tick\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"></polyline></svg></span></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__competitorCol\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__cross\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><line x1=\"18\" y1=\"6\" x2=\"6\" y2=\"18\"></line><line x1=\"6\" y1=\"6\" x2=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></span></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__competitorCol MarketingSections-module__jODscW__ourCol\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__cross\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><line x1=\"18\" y1=\"6\" x2=\"6\" y2=\"18\"></line><line x1=\"6\" y1=\"6\" x2=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></span></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__tableRow\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureLabel\">Ad Intrusion</div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__competitorCol\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__statusText \">Medium</span></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__competitorCol\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__statusText \">Extreme</span></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__competitorCol MarketingSections-module__jODscW__ourCol\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__statusText MarketingSections-module__jODscW__statusOur\">Minimal</span></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__tableRow\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureLabel\">IP Protection</div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__competitorCol\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__statusText \">None</span></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__competitorCol\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__statusText \">Partial</span></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__competitorCol MarketingSections-module__jODscW__ourCol\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__statusText MarketingSections-module__jODscW__statusOur\">Full Proxy</span></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__tableRow\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__featureLabel\">View Reels/Stories</div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__competitorCol\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__tick\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"></polyline></svg></span></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__competitorCol\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__statusText \">Sometimes</span></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__competitorCol MarketingSections-module__jODscW__ourCol\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__statusText MarketingSections-module__jODscW__statusOur\">Yes (HD)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__section\" id=\"use-cases\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__container\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__sectionHead\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__badge\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" style=\"margin-right:6px;vertical-align:middle\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"16\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"8\" x2=\"12.01\" y2=\"8\"></line></svg>Use Cases</span><h2 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__sectionTitle\">Popular Ways to View<br/><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__grad\">Instagram Anonymously</span></h2><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__sectionSub\">Whether you&#x27;re a marketer, creator, or simply privacy-conscious — here&#x27;s how people use InstaPVStory.</p></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCasesGrid\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseCard\" style=\"--acc:#06b6d4\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseTag\" style=\"color:#06b6d4;border-color:#06b6d4\">For Marketers</span><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseEmoji\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><line x1=\"18\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"18\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"4\"></line><line x1=\"6\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"6\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></span><h3 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseTitle\">Competitor Research</h3><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseDesc\">Monitor competitor profiles, track their content strategy, and analyze engagement without being noticed.</p></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseCard\" style=\"--acc:#8b5cf6\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseTag\" style=\"color:#8b5cf6;border-color:#8b5cf6\">For Creatives</span><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseEmoji\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"3\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><circle cx=\"8.5\" cy=\"8.5\" r=\"1.5\"></circle><polyline points=\"21 15 16 10 5 21\"></polyline></svg></span><h3 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseTitle\">Creative Inspiration</h3><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseDesc\">Browse aesthetics, content styles, and visual storytelling from top creators worldwide.</p></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseCard\" style=\"--acc:#10b981\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseTag\" style=\"color:#10b981;border-color:#10b981\">For Parents</span><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseEmoji\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\"></path></svg></span><h3 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseTitle\">Parental Monitoring</h3><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseDesc\">Keep an eye on public profiles your kids might interact with. Stay informed without disruption.</p></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseCard\" style=\"--acc:#f59e0b\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseTag\" style=\"color:#f59e0b;border-color:#f59e0b\">For Privacy</span><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseEmoji\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M17.94 17.94A10.07 10.07 0 0 1 12 20c-7 0-11-8-11-8a18.45 18.45 0 0 1 5.06-5.94M9.9 4.24A9.12 9.12 0 0 1 12 4c7 0 11 8 11 8a18.5 18.5 0 0 1-2.16 3.19m-6.72-1.07a3 3 0 1 1-4.24-4.24\"></path><line x1=\"1\" y1=\"1\" x2=\"23\" y2=\"23\"></line></svg></span><h3 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseTitle\">Private Browsing</h3><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseDesc\">View public profiles without leaving a &quot;seen&quot; mark or triggering profile visit notifications.</p></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseCard\" style=\"--acc:#ec4899\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseTag\" style=\"color:#ec4899;border-color:#ec4899\">For Brands</span><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseEmoji\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"7\"></circle><polyline points=\"8.21 13.89 7 23 12 20 17 23 15.79 13.88\"></polyline></svg></span><h3 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseTitle\">Influencer Vetting</h3><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseDesc\">Verify influencer metrics, authenticity, and content quality before any brand partnership.</p></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseCard\" style=\"--acc:#ef4444\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseTag\" style=\"color:#ef4444;border-color:#ef4444\">For Research</span><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseEmoji\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M4 19.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 17H20\"></path><path d=\"M6.5 2H20v20H6.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2z\"></path></svg></span><h3 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseTitle\">Social Research</h3><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__useCaseDesc\">Academics and researchers study social media trends without needing an Instagram account.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__section\" id=\"blog\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__container\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__sectionHead\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__badge\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" style=\"margin-right:6px;vertical-align:middle\"><path d=\"M4 19.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 17H20\"></path><path d=\"M6.5 2H20v20H6.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2z\"></path></svg>Latest Blog</span><h2 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__sectionTitle\">Anonymity &amp; Privacy<br/><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__grad\">Resources</span></h2><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__sectionSub\">Stay updated with the latest tips, tricks, and guides for secure social media browsing.</p></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogGrid\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogCard\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogCardImage\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611162617213-7d7a39e9b1d7?q=80&amp;w=800&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop\" alt=\"How to View Instagram Stories Anonymously (2026 Guide)\"/><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogCardDate\">April 12, 2026</span></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogCardContent\"><h3 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogCardTitle\">How to View Instagram Stories Anonymously (2026 Guide)</h3><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogCardExcerpt\">Want to watch stories without the owner knowing? Here are the best ways to stay invisible while browsing.</p><a class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogReadMore\" href=\"/blog/how-to-view-instagram-stories-anonymously\">Read Article →</a></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogCard\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogCardImage\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1563986768609-322da13575f3?q=80&amp;w=800&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop\" alt=\"Protecting Your Privacy on Instagram: Essential Tips\"/><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogCardDate\">April 10, 2026</span></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogCardContent\"><h3 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogCardTitle\">Protecting Your Privacy on Instagram: Essential Tips</h3><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogCardExcerpt\">Your data is valuable. Learn how to minimize your digital footprint on social media platforms.</p><a class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogReadMore\" href=\"/blog/protecting-your-privacy-on-instagram\">Read Article →</a></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogCard\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogCardImage\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460925895917-afdab827c52f?q=80&amp;w=800&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop\" alt=\"The Benefits of Anonymous Competitor Research\"/><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogCardDate\">April 08, 2026</span></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogCardContent\"><h3 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogCardTitle\">The Benefits of Anonymous Competitor Research</h3><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogCardExcerpt\">How staying invisible helps you gather better market intelligence for your brand.</p><a class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogReadMore\" href=\"/blog/benefits-of-anonymous-competitor-research\">Read Article →</a></div></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogArchiveCta\"><a class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__blogArchiveBtn\" href=\"/blog\">View All Posts</a></div></div></section><div style=\"text-align:center;padding:8px 24px 0\"></div><section class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__section\" id=\"testimonials\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__container\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__sectionHead\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__badge\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" style=\"margin-right:6px;vertical-align:middle\"><path d=\"M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z\"></path></svg>Testimonials</span><h2 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__sectionTitle\">What Our Users<br/><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__grad\">Are Saying</span></h2><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__sectionSub\">Trusted by marketers, creators, researchers, and everyday users around the world.</p></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialsGrid\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialCard\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stars\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg></div><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialText\">&quot;<!-- -->InstaPVStory is the cleanest Instagram viewer I&#x27;ve found. No shady ads, no login prompts — just works perfectly. Our team uses it daily for competitor analysis.<!-- -->&quot;</p><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialAuthor\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialAvatar\" style=\"background:#7c3aed\">SK</div><div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialName\">Sarah K.</div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialRole\">Digital Marketing Manager</div></div></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialCard\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stars\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg></div><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialText\">&quot;<!-- -->I was skeptical at first, but this tool is legitimately impressive. Fetches real stories and reels instantly. It&#x27;s become my go-to for content research.<!-- -->&quot;</p><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialAuthor\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialAvatar\" style=\"background:#06b6d4\">AR</div><div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialName\">Ahmed R.</div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialRole\">Content Creator</div></div></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialCard\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stars\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg></div><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialText\">&quot;<!-- -->Finally, a professional tool that respects my privacy. No sign-up, no data collection. The UI is stunning and it just works. Highly recommended.<!-- -->&quot;</p><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialAuthor\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialAvatar\" style=\"background:#10b981\">PM</div><div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialName\">Priya M.</div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialRole\">Brand Strategist</div></div></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialCard\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stars\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg></div><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialText\">&quot;<!-- -->The story viewer is absolutely unmatched. Real-time, beautiful display, and no watermarks. I use it to get inspiration from top photographers anonymously.<!-- -->&quot;</p><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialAuthor\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialAvatar\" style=\"background:#f59e0b\">JT</div><div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialName\">James T.</div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialRole\">Freelance Photographer</div></div></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialCard\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stars\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg></div><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialText\">&quot;<!-- -->Perfect for academic research. I can study public profiles, posts, and engagement patterns without disrupting the subjects or needing an account.<!-- -->&quot;</p><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialAuthor\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialAvatar\" style=\"background:#ec4899\">MJ</div><div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialName\">Mikaela J.</div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialRole\">Social Media Researcher</div></div></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialCard\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__stars\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" style=\"margin-right:4px\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg></div><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialText\">&quot;<!-- -->Built on high-performance global architecture — that alone sets it apart from every scraped, sketchy alternative. This is how a professional tool should work.<!-- -->&quot;</p><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialAuthor\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialAvatar\" style=\"background:#8b5cf6\">DC</div><div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialName\">Daniel C.</div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__testimonialRole\">Tech Entrepreneur</div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__section\" id=\"faq\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__container\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__sectionHead\"><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__badge\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" style=\"margin-right:6px;vertical-align:middle\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3\"></path><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"17\" x2=\"12.01\" y2=\"17\"></line></svg>FAQ</span><h2 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__sectionTitle\">Frequently Asked<br/><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__grad\">Questions</span></h2><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__sectionSub\">Everything you need to know about how InstaPVStory works and how we protect your privacy.</p></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqList\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqItem \"><button class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqQ\"><span>Can I view private Instagram profiles?</span><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqChevron\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"></polyline></svg></span></button><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqA\"><p>No — and that&#x27;s by design. InstaPVStory strictly accesses public profiles using official data protocols. We do not support, promote, or enable any attempt to view private accounts. Any tool claiming to do so is a scam.</p></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqItem \"><button class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqQ\"><span>Is InstaPVStory really 100% anonymous?</span><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqChevron\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"></polyline></svg></span></button><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqA\"><p>Yes. Since we access data through our own secure environment, you never log in with your personal account. The target profile has absolutely no way of knowing you viewed their content.</p></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqItem \"><button class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqQ\"><span>Do you store my search history or personal data?</span><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqChevron\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"></polyline></svg></span></button><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqA\"><p>We store recent searches locally on your own device (browser storage) for your convenience — they never leave your machine. We do not collect, transmit, or sell any user data whatsoever.</p></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqItem \"><button class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqQ\"><span>How is this different from just visiting Instagram yourself?</span><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqChevron\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"></polyline></svg></span></button><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqA\"><p>When you visit a profile on Instagram while logged in, your account is added to their visitor data. With InstaPVStory, you browse without an account, leaving no trace. It&#x27;s the difference between being invisible and being seen.</p></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqItem \"><button class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqQ\"><span>Can I watch Stories and Reels for free?</span><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqChevron\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"></polyline></svg></span></button><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqA\"><p>Yes, completely free. Stories are fetched in real-time via advanced discovery protocols. You can watch videos and view photos at full quality without paying anything or creating an account.</p></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqItem \"><button class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqQ\"><span>Why can I only view Business/Creator accounts?</span><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqChevron\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"></polyline></svg></span></button><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqA\"><p>This is a limitation of the current discovery protocols. The systems are designed to access public-facing Business and Creator accounts, which is a large majority of public profiles on the platform.</p></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqItem \"><button class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqQ\"><span>Is it legal to use InstaPVStory?</span><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqChevron\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"></polyline></svg></span></button><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqA\"><p>Yes. We exclusively access publicly available content through official data infrastructure. This is the same mechanism used by millions of third-party social media apps. We operate well within the bounds of standard data privacy terms for public information.</p></div></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqItem \"><button class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqQ\"><span>Why do some profiles show an error?</span><span class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqChevron\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"></polyline></svg></span></button><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__faqA\"><p>A profile may fail to load if: (1) it&#x27;s set to private, (2) it&#x27;s a personal account (not a Business/Creator account), or (3) the username is misspelled. Make sure the profile is a public Business or Creator account.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__ctaSection\"><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__ctaGlow\"></div><div class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__container\"><h2 class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__ctaTitle\">Start Browsing Anonymously</h2><p class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__ctaSub\">No signup. No login. No limits. Just enter a username and go.</p><a href=\"#search\" class=\"MarketingSections-module__jODscW__ctaBtn\">Try It Free →</a></div></section></div></main><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"Footer-module__hP-FLq__footer\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"Footer-module__hP-FLq__content\"><div class=\"Footer-module__hP-FLq__brand\"><div class=\"Footer-module__hP-FLq__brandTitle\"><div class=\"Footer-module__hP-FLq__logoIcon\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"4\" fill=\"white\" opacity=\"0.95\"></circle><path d=\"M4 20c0-4 3.6-7 8-7s8 3 8 7\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" opacity=\"0.8\"></path></svg></div><h3 style=\"color:#ffffff;margin:0\">InstaPvStory</h3></div><p class=\"text-small\">Anonymous Instagram story and highlight viewer.</p></div><div class=\"Footer-module__hP-FLq__links\"><div class=\"Footer-module__hP-FLq__group\"><h4>Company</h4><a class=\"text-small\" href=\"/about\">About Us</a><a class=\"text-small\" href=\"/features\">Features</a><a class=\"text-small\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></div><div class=\"Footer-module__hP-FLq__group\"><h4>Legal</h4><a class=\"text-small\" href=\"/terms\">Terms of Service</a><a class=\"text-small\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy Policy</a><a class=\"text-small\" href=\"/disclaimer\">Disclaimer</a></div><div class=\"Footer-module__hP-FLq__group\"><h4>Support</h4><a class=\"text-small\" href=\"/contact\">Contact Us</a><a class=\"text-small\" href=\"/#faq\">FAQ</a></div></div></div><div class=\"Footer-module__hP-FLq__bottom\"><p class=\"text-small\">© <!-- -->2024<!-- --> InstaPvStory. All rights reserved.</p></div></div></footer></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0yb2wil16uz6h.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[68504,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0xfb.q6up~c0w.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n3:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0xfb.q6up~c0w.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n4:I[37457,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0xfb.q6up~c0w.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n6:I[97367,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0xfb.q6up~c0w.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"OutletBoundary\\\"]\\n7:\\\"$Sreact.suspense\\\"\\n9:I[97367,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0xfb.q6up~c0w.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"ViewportBoundary\\\"]\\nb:I[97367,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0xfb.q6up~c0w.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn